title: Ep. 834 - Jethalal Sneaks In - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal is curious to know if Sunderlal has perfectly concluded his assigned work. He tried sneaking into the renovation but security didn't allow him to. Everyone is set to see the renovated society and also wish Happy New Year to each other.

title: Ep. 835 - Champaklal Calls Special Guests - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal decides to call special guests for the opening ceremony. Tapu Sena ask Popatlal not to call any additional celebrity.  Everyone waits for the guests at the gate.

title: Ep. 836 - Gokuldham's New Look - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone is happy to see the well constructed society. However, Bhide comes up with a doubt that the notice board should have kept somewhere else. The last wing, Jethalal's wing, is left to be seen. Sunder is already worried.

title: Ep. 837 - Sunder Is Screwed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal is shocked to see the missing stairs that could led him to his home. Sunder comes up with a backup plan which eventually fails. Society discusses about the good memories spent in Gokuldham.

title: Ep. 838 - Gokuldham Turns Mini India - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Priests from different religions visit Gokuldham to bless the society. Society asks them to perform rituals before they enter into their new renovated home.

title: Ep. 839 - Disco Dance Competition - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sunder has decided to gift a car for the one who wins the disco dance competition. Everyone gears up for it. A dance teacher is assigned to help them practice disco dance.

title: Ep. 840 - Dance Teacher Unconscious - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Dance teacher falls unconscious as he couldn't bear Dr. Hathi's weight. However, he is brought to senses. Popatlal asks to cancel the competition.

title: Ep. 841 - Disco Night - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Maddy sir surprises everyone by inviting Saroj Khan as the judge for the night. Saroj Khan shares her funny moments with Gokuldham. Dr. Hathi is called upon the stage to perform first.

title: Ep. 842 - Popatlal Tries Negotiating - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is called next for his performance. He asks Saroj Khan to give him full scores in order to win the prize to which she refused. Sodhi, also, asks Saroj to give him good scores. Bhide is worried as he has not got his disco costumes yet.

title: Ep. 843 - An Unexpected Entry - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone is worried as society runs out of electricity in between their show. Unexpectedly Baga and Natu Kaka mark their entry with full energy surprising the crowd. Taarak seeks blessings from Saroj before they leave for their performance.

title: Ep. 844 - Garba And Disco Together - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Saroj Khan asks Jetha and Daya to perform garba with the same disco song. Later, she mentions how brilliant their performance was. Bhide and Madhvi are worried as their turn was about to come yet they haven't received their costumes yet.

title: Ep. 845- Bhide's Mix-Matched Costume - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Since Bhide's costume didn't arrive so Madhvi suggested him to borrow different costumes from the former participants. They rock the stage together. Saroj Khan decides to distribute awards from her side before she announces the winner.

title: Ep. 846 - Iyer Goes Mad - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Finally the winner is announced i.e., Iyer and Babita so Iyer dances crazily. Later Saroj Khan reveals that Jetha and Daya, Iyer and Babita have the same scores so they have a face off. They dance their heart out.

title: Ep. 847 - Jetha Is Upset - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer and Babita manage to win the competition. Jetha feels defeated and is sad. Everyone starts cheering for the winners. Jethalal doesn't let Daya cheer for them. Mona asks them to issue a cheque of 25 lakhs in order to get the car.

title: Ep. 848 - Daya And Jetha Fight - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is tired after the disco night and decides to take a bath. Daya insists to take a bath first but Jethalal finds a way to take Daya out. Jetha waits for Babita in the balcony to wish her good morning but he doesn't get a chance.
